<br>
  Just wanted to take a little bit of time to voice my concerns about the impact on the new FFA (or FCFS or whatever you wanna call it) system that the server has gone too.<br>
  Now Im far from an Uber character, and I'll be the first to admit theres ALOT of higher lvl stuff that I dont know anything about, all im commenting on here is my personal experiences in these areas.<br>
  From what I can tell (I may be wrong) is that the big conflict with PoH and PoF was that higher lvl guilds couldnt get into them to kill the God mobs and such for thier Epic pieces, reason being these mobs only spawn every 7 days, so with the old resevation system you would wait 3 months or so and hope the mob would be up in the 3 days alloted. Now I can see the valid gripe there, its silly for these guilds to have to wait this long to only hope the one mob they need is up (planar armor being basically worthless to them) Now, with FFA, this first problem has been solved, cuz now after a patch, these high lvl guilds will get online,get oranized and go in and kill said mob and be done with it...no problem right? wrong.<br>
  The problem arrises with the other 6 days of the week. There are very few Guilds that can get online as a single unit, zone into a plane and clear it with any sort of effeciency. the problem is these guilds DONT need Hate/Fear on the days the gods arent up. The rest of us need to plan out in advance, and usually get the help from friends, or other guilds to be able to do it, and the more people that you add to a group that dont know each other or havent worked together b4 adds more room for disaster. <br>
   At first I thought to myself that this system was great..I could go into Hate and camp there and get a full set of my Hate armor and I'd be gtg, well after 3 nights there...I discovered I was dead wrong, the first 2 nights went smooth enough with Roluvan and Brice pulling, we managed to clear out alot of mobs and get some armor drops for people, and everyone was having a good time, then random people start logging in and wanting in on the riads and such and it soon got outta control (example, 1 night was 29 people in zone 12 which were warriors) and even worse whole raid groups will show up and try to hold seperate raids in the same area which equals mass amounts of trains and death for all those involved..<br>
   Fear is a bit different but similar at the same time...since most Fear gear tends to drop at the same time, people tend to be online when those mobs are being pulled and mysteriously are gone after those mobs are done...Now this is wrong IMO but what the hell can you do about it now? Half the people there now dont even know each other.<br>
   Anyway, Ill cut this off because im rambling now, but I hope any that read this can see the point Im trying to get at.....that being, with the new FFA, Hate and Fear are basically screwed for the people who really need it (ie for armor) <br>
   Let me also say that Im not trying to whine about not being able to get Gear (Dont care now really, I got some purdy orange stuff now anways =) But more so to present what I perceive to be a problem. Unfortunately I cant present a solution to this, because if was even to mention the word &quot;reservation&quot; Id prolly be stoned to death....<br>
   Also Im sure theres many of you that dont give a rat's ass as to what my opinion is, and thats fine too, to each their own I say, but with the server growing every day (with no split on the horizon) and more and more 46+ characters coming down the line, I see this as a problem that wont go away, but just get bigger =( I just know theres gotta be a better way to handle PoH and PoF that will benifit the whole Quellious community.<br>
<br>
